  "faqA1": "Pick a subject, tap play, and the timer tracks your current session while adding it to that subject's total time. Tap pause any time to stop and save your progress.",
  "faqQ2": "What is the break countdown?",
  "faqA2": "Each session follows a classic Pomodoro cycle: a 25 minute countdown to your next break. When it reaches zero it simply resets, it's a reminder, not a hard stop.",
  "faqQ3": "How do I add a new subject?",
  "faqA3": "Open a category from Home, then tap \"Add Subject\" at the bottom of the list. You can pick a color and set an estimated hours goal for it.",
  "faqQ4": "How are groups and the leaderboard calculated?",
  "faqA4": "Groups show a scoreboard of everyone's studied hours. Switch between Today, This Week and This Month to see who studied the most in that period.",
  "faqQ5": "Can I change the app's color theme?",
  "faqA5": "Yes, go to Settings > My Profile and pick any theme color. Every gradient, button and highlight across the app updates to match it, including dark mode.",

